{"tid":200784,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"輸金像獎冇失落　坤坤願為好戲犧牲露蛋","createTime":"2017-04-14T09:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T14:03:05.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b1eb852c159726839fa2957bb5c31caf3c7d31c7","tid":200784,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:10:27.000Z","msg":"藝人吳業坤到銅鑼灣為英皇電影《幸運是我》謝票，談到失落金像獎「最佳新演員」，他說：「冇失落，Day 1已經講緊我係墊屍底，能夠得到評委嘅支持，已經覺得好榮幸，紅姐（惠英紅）好好人，請我哋食飯，我都戥佢攞影后開心。我希望之後都可以多啲參與電影圈，拍多啲好電影。（為咗電影可以好似梁朝偉咁露蛋蛋？）得！露埋蛋黃都得呀！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170413/photo/bkn-20170413231917715-0413_00862_001_01b.jpg?20170414015416\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170413%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170413231917715-0413_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20170414015416&h=93362013&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c36a66066be013f6d7dc3c00b63c6a1c10db724","tid":200784,"uid":182334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:03:05.000Z","msg":"犠牲觀眾"}]}